    <h2>1. Heading & Paragraphs</h2>
    <p>I love traveling to new places, seeing different cultures, and trying yummy food. Below are a few places I dream about visiting.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>2. Text Formatting</h2>
    <p><b>Bold:</b> I really want to go to Japan.</p>
    <p><i>Italic:</i> Italy has delicious food!</p>
    <p><u>Underlined:</u> Australia is full of cool animals.</p>
    <p><strong>Strong:</strong> I must go to New York someday!</p>
    <p><em>Emphasized:</em> The beaches in Hawaii look beautiful.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>3. Images with Attributes</h2>
